<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shegviqʼvara chven</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shegviqʼvara chven
 rom mistsa mkholodshobili dze
 man chvens tavze
 tmats kʼi datvala
 datvala tsremli tvalze

[C1]
   aba ras dainanebs
   prtebze sheskhmuls gvatʼarebs

[V2]
 mogvitsʼoda migvigho gagvtsʼminda dagvaqʼena
 gvtskho tavisi sulit
 da gvitsʼoda ekʼlesia

[V3]
 aghtkma dagvido:
 ar shegeshindet
 rotsa tsetskhlshi gaivlit
 ar dagtsʼvavt ali
 me tkventana var
 upali tsʼminda tkveni

